= #metrics-wizard Configuration

== Configuration Details:
. This configuration contains metrics discovery poll interval and reporter specific configuration
... MBeans-discovery-poll-interval: Poll time to discover and update the mbeans
... reporter: The type of reporter to push the metrics and the reporter specific configuration

== The example configuration

[source,yaml]
.metrics-wizard.yml for console reporter
----
MBeans-discovery-poll-interval: 5 # in seconds
reporter:
    type: console
    durationUnit: milliseconds
    frequency: 2 minutes
    timeZone: UTC
    output: stdout
----

.metrics-wizard.yml for datadog reporter with UDP transport
----
MBeans-discovery-poll-interval: 5 # in seconds
reporter:
    type: datadog
    transport:
      type: udp
      statsdHost: "localhost"
      port: 8125
----
.metrics-wizard.yml for datadog reporter with HTTP transport
----
MBeans-discovery-poll-interval: 5 # in seconds
reporter:
    type: datadog
    transport:
      type: http
      apiKey: abc123
      connectTimeout: 10 seconds
      socketTimeout: 10 seconds
----